    "headline": "New Survey Shows HPV Awareness Isn't Keeping Pace with Certain HPV-Related Cancer Trends in Canada",
    "summary": "Merck (NYSE: MRK), known as MSD outside the United States and Canada, has released new data examining Canadians' knowledge of human papillomavirus (HPV) across age, gender, and regional groups. The survey revealed notable gaps in awareness—particularly among men and younger adults—even as rates of certain HPV‑related cancers continue to rise across the country.",
